  <entry>
    <title>捐躯赴国难,视死忽如归</title>
    <link href="https://lucas-nz.github.io/posts/451bd757/"/>
    <id>https://lucas-nz.github.io/posts/451bd757/</id>
    <published>2020-09-18T00:58:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-18T03:00:30.467Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting/img/%E5%8B%BF%E5%BF%98%E5%9B%BD%E8%80%BB%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%85%AB%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%98.png" loading="lazy"></p><hide><h6 id="英文原文"><a href="#英文原文" class="headerlink" title="英文原文"></a>英文原文</h6></hide><gm-en><p>Giving up his life for the sake of his country,</p><p>he looks toward death as a journey home.</p><a id="more"></a></gm-en><hide><h6 id="中文译文"><a href="#中文译文" class="headerlink" title="中文译文"></a>中文译文</h6></hide><gm-cn><p>捐躯赴国难, 视死忽如归.</p></gm-cn><ref><p> ——曹植《白马篇》（吴伏生译）</p><mark><p>摘抄自中国日报双语新闻公众号</p></mark></ref><blockquote><p>国耻定铭记, 我辈当自强.</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting/img/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%E5%8F%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%8F%B7.jpg" loading="lazy"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting/img/%E5%8B%BF%E5%BF%98%E5%9B%BD%E8%80%BB%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%85%AB%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%98.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hide&gt;

&lt;h6 id=&quot;英文原文&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#英文原文&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;英文原文&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;英文原文&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/hide&gt;

&lt;gm-en&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Giving up his life for the sake of his country,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;he looks toward death as a journey home.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
