  <entry>
    <title>小朋友, 你是否有很多问号?</title>
    <link href="https://lucas-nz.github.io/posts/f9398168/"/>
    <id>https://lucas-nz.github.io/posts/f9398168/</id>
    <published>2020-09-17T00:58:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-18T02:47:59.887Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting//img/%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B,%E4%BD%A0%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E9%97%AE%E5%8F%B7.png" style="zoom:70%;" / loading="lazy"><hide><h6 id="英文原文"><a href="#英文原文" class="headerlink" title="英文原文"></a>英文原文</h6></hide><gm-en><p>If we would have new Knowledge,</p><p>We would get a whole world of new questions.</p><a id="more"></a></gm-en><hide><h6 id="中文译文"><a href="#中文译文" class="headerlink" title="中文译文"></a>中文译文</h6></hide><gm-cn><p>想要获得新知识, 就必须提出大量的问题.</p></gm-cn><ref><p> ——美国哲学家苏珊·兰格（Susanne Langer）</p><mark><p>摘抄自中国日报双语新闻公众号</p></mark></ref><blockquote><p>学而不思则罔,  思而不学则殆</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting/img/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%E5%8F%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%8F%B7.jpg" loading="lazy"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting//img/%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B,%E4%BD%A0%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E9%97%AE%E5%8F%B7.png&quot; style=&quot;zoom:70%;&quot; /&gt;

&lt;hide&gt;

&lt;h6 id=&quot;英文原文&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#英文原文&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;英文原文&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;英文原文&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/hide&gt;

&lt;gm-en&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If we would have new Knowledge,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We would get a whole world of new questions.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
