    <published>2020-09-11T04:01:11.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-18T02:47:55.190Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting//img/%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%95%E9%9A%85,%E5%BF%83%E5%90%91%E7%92%80%E7%92%A8.jpg" alt="生于井隅,心向璀璨" style="zoom: 70%;" / loading="lazy"><hide><h6 id="英文原文"><a href="#英文原文" class="headerlink" title="英文原文"></a>英文原文</h6></hide><gm-en><p>We are all in the gutter,</p><p>but some of us are looking at the stars.</p><a id="more"></a></gm-en><hide><h6 id="中文译文"><a href="#中文译文" class="headerlink" title="中文译文"></a>中文译文</h6></hide><gm-cn><p>生于井隅, 心向璀璨</p></gm-cn><ref><p> ————爱尔兰作家 奥斯卡·王尔德</p><mark><p>摘抄自中国日报双语新闻公众号</p></mark></ref><blockquote><p>愿生活有柴米油盐, 也有花前月下.</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting/img/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%E5%8F%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%8F%B7.jpg" loading="lazy"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucas-nz/ImgHosting//img/%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%95%E9%9A%85,%E5%BF%83%E5%90%91%E7%92%80%E7%92%A8.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;生于井隅,心向璀璨&quot; style=&quot;zoom: 70%;&quot; /&gt;

&lt;hide&gt;

&lt;h6 id=&quot;英文原文&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#英文原文&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;英文原文&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;英文原文&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/hide&gt;

&lt;gm-en&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are all in the gutter,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;but some of us are looking at the stars.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
